0_Heat <I>1_oil</I> 2_in 3_a 4_10-inch 5_heavy 6_skillet 7_over 8_moderate 9_heat 10_until 11_hot 12_but 13_not 14_smoking. 15_Add <I>16_carrots</I> 17_and 18_saut, 19_stirring 20_occasionally, 21_5 22_minutes. 23_Add <I>24_pomegranate 25_juice,</I> <I>26_cinnamon 27_stick,</I> <I>28_salt,</I> 29_and <I>30_pepper</I> 31_and 32_simmer, 33_uncovered, 34_stirring 35_occasionally, 36_until <I>37_carrots</I> 38_are 39_tender 40_and <I>41_liquid</I> 42_is 43_reduced 44_to 45_a <I>46_glaze,</I> 47_20 48_to 49_25 50_minutes. 51_Add <I>52_coriander 53_seeds</I> 54_and 55_cook, 56_stirring, 57_1 58_minute. 59_Discard <I>60_cinnamon 61_stick</I> 62_and 63_serve <I>64_carrots</I> 65_hot 66_or 67_at 68_room 69_temperature. 
